stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> open : Finding emitted by engine<br/>(evidence required)

    open --> triaged : Operator reviews<br/>dispatch_queue_item

    triaged --> in_progress : CAT agent role<br/>accepts dispatch item

    in_progress --> mitigated : Remediation applied<br/>but root cause unconfirmed

    in_progress --> resolved : Root cause confirmed<br/>and fix verified

    mitigated --> resolved : Monitoring confirms<br/>issue closed

    open --> dismissed : Finding determined<br/>to be a false positive

    triaged --> dismissed : Evidence insufficient<br/>after triage

    resolved --> [*]
    dismissed --> [*]

    note right of open
        finding_id assigned
        evidence linked
        dispatch item queued
        status = "open"
    end note

    note right of in_progress
        agent_role assigned
        acceptance_criteria active
        stop_condition monitored
    end note
